    Library

    public static class Library.ClauseCounts
extends java.util.TreeMap
    The Library's ClauseCounts class is a TreeMap with structure: LangName:kinTerm => Counter[] (cumulative counts of string length). It holds the ClauseCounts file contents during a session.
